  "vnet_info": "Hub VNet: 10.0.0.0/16 (AzureFirewallSubnet: 10.0.1.0/26, AzureBastionSubnet: 10.0.2.0/26, GatewaySubnet: 10.0.3.0/27) | Spoke VNet: 10.1.0.0/16 (pe-subnet: 10.1.1.0/24, workload-subnet: 10.1.2.0/24) | Hub-Spoke Peering 연결",
  "hierarchy": [
